feed.title: Eta Kappa Nu - Epsilon Phi
feed.subtitle: IEEE-Eta Kappa Nu (HKN) is the student honor society under IEEE dedicated to encouraging and acknowledging excellence in the fields of Electrical Engineering, Computer Engineering and other IEEE fields of interest. The organization offers a variety of service programs and leadership training to help student members develop lifelong skills that differentiate them from others seeking prominent positions in industry and academia.
